| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3956 — Mass File Rename (meow)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 21fcb9fe-a4d8-510e-8bdd-d50e00aa3cd3"
